To make your application Tecla Accessible follow this procedure:

1. Include the package ca.idi.tecla.lib in your application.
2. Create an instance of the class InputAccess say inputAccess giving the activity under consideration as a parameter to its constructor.
3. Make sure you override the onPause() and onResume() methods in your activity.
4. Add the line inputAccess.onPause() to the overriden onPause() method and inputAccess.onResume() to the overriden onResume() method in your activity.
5. Add the return statement inputAccess.onPrepareOptionsMenu(menu) to the method public boolean onPrepareOptionsMenu(Menu); in your activity, if you dont have any such method create one.

Note:
1. Method InputAccess.onPrepareOptionsMenu is overloaded